<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="100" b="1" /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真抱歉，<delay20 />
我現在想一個人靜一靜<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay40 />
<anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />能不能先別管我呢？<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><endTag a="100" b="1" /></message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="100" b="1" /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你先不要管我<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay40 />
<anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我現在需要時間<delay20 />
一個人好好思考<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><endTag a="100" b="1" /></message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="100" b="1" /><anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我現在不想跟任何人說話<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay40 />
<anim id="SadSpiral" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你應該也曾經有過<delay20 />
像這樣心情低落的時候吧？<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><endTag a="100" b="1" /></message>
	<message label="100" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="100" b="1" /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這附近盛開的花兒<delay20 />
都已經枯萎了呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><endTag a="100" b="1" /></message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="100" b="1" /><anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然之前並不是我在照顧那些花兒，<delay20 />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是<delay8 />我好像也在不知不覺中<delay20 />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />受到那些花兒們很大的鼓舞呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><endTag a="100" b="1" /></message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="100" b="1" /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是我能早點注意到，幫忙澆個水就好了。<delay40 />
<anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />人總是在失去之後，<delay20 />才會發現失去的東西
對自己有多重要呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><endTag a="100" b="1" /></message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />曾經跟我說過<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />「植物即使沒有每天澆水，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其實<delay8 />也可以長得很好」這句話<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以我才會一時鬆懈，沒仔細注意……<delay40 />
<anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />結果某一天等我發現時，<delay8 />
花兒已經失去活力了<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="103_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="player" targetSpec="" />真是遺憾呢……</message>
	<message label="103_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="player" targetSpec="" />原來是這樣啊</message>
	<message label="104" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay40 />
雖然我急急忙忙澆了水，<delay20 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但好像已經有點太遲了<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然植物不需要每天澆水，<delay20 />
但我也應該至少每兩天
就澆一次水的<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="105" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="100" b="1" /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我最後一次澆水到底是什麼時候呢？<delay8 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真的完全想不起來耶<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay40 />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我真是對不起花兒們……<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><endTag a="100" b="1" /></message>
	<message label="200" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="100" b="1" /><anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />唉<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay40 />
我現在沒有心情聊天<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay40 />
<anim id="SadSpiral" target="actor" targetSpec="" />暫時讓我一個人靜一靜吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><endTag a="100" b="1" /></message>
	<message label="201" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="100" b="1" /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我現在誰都不想見……<delay40 />
<anim id="SadSpiral" target="actor" targetSpec="" />請暫時讓我一個人<delay20 />
好好靜一靜吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><endTag a="100" b="1" /></message>
	<message label="202" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="100" b="1" /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我現在什麼都不想聽。<delay40 />
<anim id="SadSpiral" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我的內心<delay20 />充滿了悲傷……<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><endTag a="100" b="1" /></message>
	<message label="203" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="SadSpiral" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我的悲傷無比深沉，<delay20 />
就好像我的內心<delay8 />
被濃霧籠罩了一般<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="203_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="player" targetSpec="" />對不起</message>
	<message label="203_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="player" targetSpec="" />好吧……</message>
	<message label="204" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />既然你都道歉了，<delay20 />
這次我就原諒你好了<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay40 />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但你可不能再做同樣的事了喔？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="205" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果你已經在反省了，<delay20 />
那這次我就原諒你吧。<delay40 />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是只有這次，<delay8 />下不為例喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>